SUMMARY:Lyric Theatre:  ARMONIA\, Excellence in Flamenco
DESCRIPTION:TORONTO ARTS & CULTURE\n**Esmeralda Enrique Spanish Dance Comp
 any** \\| Academy of Spanish Dance:\n\n*Ticket link is below* (20% off pro
 mo)--\n\nFlamenco is Life. It's a living art.\n\n***Special guests\, accla
 imed flamenco dancer José Manuel Álvarez (Barcelona\, Spain) and beloved
  singer Manuel Soto (Jerez\, Spain)\,*** join dancers Kiyo Asaoka\, Makeda
  Benítez\, Pamela Briz\, Nancy Cardwell\, Virginia Castro Durán\, Rocío
  Conde\, Alison MacDonald\, and as always\, Artistic Director Esmeralda En
 rique\, with flamenco guitarists\, Caroline Planté (Montréal) and Benjam
 in Barrile (Toronto)\, singer Marcos Marín (Montréal) with percussionist
 \, Miguel Medina (Montréal).\n\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5IeTi_ZxU
 GU\n\n**Ticket link:**\n\nhttps://www.flamencos.net/ (You are purchasing f
 or Friday May 8th)\n\nOnce you enter Ticketmaster link (May 8th)--look for
  the **UNLOCK** box\n\n**Enter promo code:** MEETUP\n\nThis will give you 
 a 20% off ticket price.\n\nPlay around with the seating chart--but more th
 an likely you can find a $40-$45 ticket (be patient!)
