SUMMARY:OTTAWA: Culture in the Capital    (8th annual visit)
DESCRIPTION:TORONTO ARTS & CULTURE\nCan you join us in **Ottawa**?\n\n*For
  our annual culture long weekend! **Our 8th year.***\n\nDates/details are 
 now FIRM--thinking about early summer Culture!\n\nPLEASE read everything o
 ver before signing up--all the details are here.\n\nAs optimism builds for
  a different year (more comfortable) in 2026 then we had in previous years
 --we will continue to explore the culture scene in some of our favorite Ci
 ties. **A deep dive/below the surface.**\n\nEach year we bounce back and f
